  "body": "### Description\n\nIt would be nice if `@BeforeAll` annotated methods would be able to call REST endpoints of the Quarkus application under test using REST Assured just like in `@Test` annotated methods. This currently works but paths have to be specified differently, because the Quarkus test framework hasn't yet initialized REST Assured at this point (this is currently being done in `io.quarkus.test.junit.QuarkusTestExtension#beforeEach()`.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
